               <p>PETER - . On Friday night I was in my master's house; I saw something between this mans jacket and waistcoat. Mrs. Shelton insisted upon seeing it; he pulled out an old nose bag, afterwards he pulled out this bag; when he was at the watchhouse he did not behave as he ought to do, to ask master's pardon.</p>
               <p>The property produced and identified.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was carrying coals up stairs into the kitchen; I kicked my foot against the bag on the stairs, I took it up.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18090215-67-verdict368" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090215-67-verdict368" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
